The Challenge Definition Matrix helps managers shift their focus from field-level incidents to core organizational management issues:‚Äč

 ‚Äč

The Four Quadrants in the Snow Leopard Scenario:‚Äč

 ‚Äč

Quadrant 1 ‚Äď Single Crime Incident: Authorities discover the carcass of a single snow leopard that has been shot. Field teams conduct a criminal investigation into this specific case.‚Äč

