The Manager‚Äôs Role in this Scenario:‚Äč

Instead of merely focusing on the investigation of one dead leopard (Quadrant 1), the tool directs managers toward high-impact actions:‚Äč

 ‚Äč

Identifying the Mission: The manager‚Äôs primary task is to address the issue in Quadrant 4 to prevent future killings.‚Äč

